{"tid":1148284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸駕車時玩電話遭舉報　停牌半年兼罰款","createTime":"2019-05-10T11:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T11:22:24.000Z","uid":195617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"78dbde5600dc593d1c90b449cf2d725ecc58531c","tid":1148284,"uid":195617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/327291/碧咸駕車時玩電話遭舉報-停牌半年兼罰款\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F327291%2F%E7%A2%A7%E5%92%B8%E9%A7%95%E8%BB%8A%E6%99%82%E7%8E%A9%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E9%81%AD%E8%88%89%E5%A0%B1-%E5%81%9C%E7%89%8C%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%BC%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=714ed958\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/327291/碧咸駕車時玩電話遭舉報-停牌半年兼罰款</a><br />\n<br />\n英國媒體報道，有目擊者2018年11月21日在倫敦市區一條街道上，看到碧咸在駕駛一部賓利（Bentley）汽車時使用電話，該目擊者拍下照片，並作出舉報。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gmMCfJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgmMCfJO.png&h=0e72c710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n碧咸之後承認違規，至周四（9日）法庭裁決，碧咸須扣6分及罰款。由於碧咸之前已曾因2次駕駛超速行為而被扣6分，故此現在被扣分數累積至12分，造成要停牌半年。<br />\n<br />\n法官表示，留意到碧咸當時駕車的速度並不快，但是仍然會對他人造成危險，故此碧咸要即時停牌半年，期間不可以駕駛車輛或電單車。<br />\n<br />\n44歲的碧咸曾是英格蘭國家隊隊長，曾效力英國曼聯、西班牙皇家馬德里等球會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVnFdvt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVnFdvt.png&h=febe85b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNyQAKn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNyQAKn.png&h=a04e100c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c25fdb0b016d4314712fbd5d4b451eb1c81550b","tid":1148284,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:18:08.000Z","msg":"happy , you drive"},{"pid":"eeb9a14fa78c429bee2567b9f47105dd1b5c5b91","tid":1148284,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"呢啲係曼聯精神"}]}